If you wanna believe
the good book it says

01:44.738 --> 01:47.206
crazy began with Adam and Eve.

01:47.208 --> 01:49.475
Followed by Kane versus Abel.

01:49.477 --> 01:51.343
Sins crouching at the door.

01:52.446 --> 01:55.280
Kane lures his brother,
kills him in the field.

01:56.684 --> 01:57.950
Don't know what's so good

01:57.951 --> 01:59.351
about a book with
stories like that.

02:00.421 --> 02:02.154
It's not so much what you say

02:02.155 --> 02:03.888
about this crazy
world, or what you do.

02:37.491 --> 02:38.491
Come in.

02:52.540 --> 02:56.808
Your angel door
knocker is so beautiful.

02:56.810 --> 02:59.545
I feel better already.

02:59.547 --> 03:01.947
Yes, every door
should have one.

03:03.384 --> 03:04.416
Can I help you, miss?

03:04.418 --> 03:05.418
If you dare.

03:12.760 --> 03:14.359
Come on, Doctor.

03:23.804 --> 03:25.537
Doctor, by the smell of things,

03:25.539 --> 03:27.673
I can see that it's
your lunch hour.

03:28.909 --> 03:31.643
But if you could please give
me the hour of your time.

03:32.646 --> 03:33.946
I really need it.

03:34.915 --> 03:36.548
That is highly
irregular, Jane,

03:36.550 --> 03:38.984
I'm not familiar
with your history.

03:38.986 --> 03:40.652
Please.

03:40.654 --> 03:42.921
I don't wanna hurt myself.

03:43.991 --> 03:45.457
Or anybody else.

04:07.881 --> 04:09.348
If you insist.

04:23.497 --> 04:27.699
So this is the shrink lab
where the sick are reborn.

04:31.305 --> 04:32.471
Sad, really.

04:42.316 --> 04:44.850
Thank you so much for
seeing me, Doctor.

04:46.020 --> 04:47.519
You're saving my life.

04:53.327 --> 04:54.359
Should I lie?

04:56.530 --> 04:58.463
Or should I sit?

05:02.202 --> 05:04.736
There are no rules,
Jane, just be comfortable.

05:12.012 --> 05:14.379
Christina said that
you knew her soul

05:15.749 --> 05:18.817
and nobody else could get
into her the way that you did.

05:22.489 --> 05:24.823
How did you get
into her like that?

05:27.795 --> 05:28.827
I didn't.

05:31.899 --> 05:32.831
It was all just...

05:32.833 --> 05:34.533
You, you did.

05:35.969 --> 05:38.503
How do you get into
anybody like that?

05:40.107 --> 05:43.108
Tell me, Doctor,
what's your secret?

05:44.511 --> 05:48.847
Well, I acutely
investigate what's deeply

05:48.849 --> 05:52.718
bothering my patient and
use interesting tools

05:52.720 --> 05:55.554
to help that patient
free of that bother.

05:55.556 --> 05:56.722
All in an hour.

05:58.692 --> 06:01.109
Well, yes.

06:01.110 --> 06:03.527
Once I win over their
goodwill it's over in an hour.

06:04.998 --> 06:10.135
Well, I guess I better shut
up and let you get started.

06:14.742 --> 06:18.410
We're gonna start by me
giving you some suggestions

06:18.412 --> 06:25.550
to put you into an imaginative
role enactment mental state.

06:25.953 --> 06:27.819
Are you talking
about hypnosis?

06:29.022 --> 06:31.757
You know, Doctor,
you're freaking me out.

06:32.760 --> 06:36.695
All hypnosis really
is is self-hypnosis.

06:37.965 --> 06:40.899
I just help you put
yourself into a progressive

06:40.901 --> 06:44.703
relaxation state of heightened
suggestibility, that's all.

06:45.773 --> 06:48.907
So please, lean back and relax.

06:57.618 --> 07:00.652
Now, look into the
cuckoo hologram,

07:02.122 --> 07:05.524
nothing but the hologram.

07:07.528 --> 07:08.528
Very good.

07:10.464 --> 07:13.465
Now with every word I say to you

07:13.467 --> 07:17.769
you will become more
and more relaxed.

07:20.140 --> 07:21.140
Good.

07:22.810 --> 07:25.010
First your pupils will contract.

07:27.648 --> 07:29.548
Good, perfect.

07:30.617 --> 07:32.684
Then they will dilate.

07:34.655 --> 07:35.655
Excellent.

07:36.824 --> 07:40.225
Now they will assume
a wavy motion.

07:45.499 --> 07:50.035
And as I move the hologram
closer to your eyes,

07:50.037 --> 07:57.175
the lids will get very
very heavy and close.

08:04.051 --> 08:05.051
Excellent.

08:12.593 --> 08:17.262
Now, Jane, take this
pencil and rub it over

08:18.665 --> 08:23.702
the textured surface and
interpret the phantom image.

08:36.950 --> 08:42.020
This is known as
Paranoid Critical Method.

08:43.957 --> 08:46.992
The mind will evoke
unconscious acts.

08:51.765 --> 08:54.232
Now, Jane, put the
pencil down and tell

08:54.234 --> 08:56.234
me what you see
that bothers you.

09:01.174 --> 09:02.307
I see you.

09:14.922 --> 09:18.623
Tell me what you see
that bothers you about me.

09:21.795 --> 09:23.061
I see your suffering.

09:26.199 --> 09:27.899
I need to end it.

09:28.936 --> 09:29.936
Excuse me?

09:37.744 --> 09:38.744
To be...

09:43.650 --> 09:44.816
or not to be.

09:50.757 --> 09:51.757
Interesting.

09:53.894 --> 09:58.663
Jane, tell me, how do you
feel about your sexuality?

10:02.235 --> 10:05.837
How do you feel about
my sexuality, Doctor?

10:17.918 --> 10:19.718
Does this excite you?

10:21.722 --> 10:22.722
Um.

10:23.690 --> 10:24.690
Jane.

10:26.126 --> 10:27.993
Do you hear that music?

10:30.197 --> 10:32.931
It's our hearts
pounding in desire.

10:35.869 --> 10:42.007
My precious caress is
more savory than honey.

10:44.411 --> 10:48.279
My warm lustful
body touching yours.

10:53.954 --> 10:56.421
Seems like a dream, but is it?

11:02.262 --> 11:03.262
Um.

11:11.171 --> 11:14.706
Feel the raging blood
pumping into my bosom.

11:16.009 --> 11:19.277
Filling it, perky.

11:19.279 --> 11:21.713
And firm, soft, and hard.

11:25.052 --> 11:30.188
Erotically filling my
veins wayward down lower.

11:33.727 --> 11:37.062
Down into my trembling thighs.

11:37.064 --> 11:40.165
Down into every man's
greatest desire.

11:42.002 --> 11:44.302
A desire to do
something forbidden.

11:48.875 --> 11:52.077
Something forbidden
to stop the pain.

12:00.153 --> 12:05.023
The need is so strong
it is hypnotizing.

12:07.961 --> 12:14.099
Yearning to surrender
to become one with me.

12:15.068 --> 12:16.835
To stroke my wounds.

12:22.476 --> 12:24.909
The yearning is so great.

12:28.315 --> 12:31.950
The yearning to surrender
to become one with me.

12:43.396 --> 12:47.465
To die, to save no more.

12:48.535 --> 12:51.402
For in that dream
what's they make 'em.

13:14.394 --> 13:15.394
Wait.

13:24.037 --> 13:28.139
For in that sleep of
death, dreams will come.

14:10.483 --> 14:12.483
How do you think you got me?

14:12.485 --> 14:13.484
What?

14:50.991 --> 14:54.592
When we have shuffled
off this mortal coil.

15:03.670 --> 15:05.470
Must give us pause.

15:44.511 --> 15:45.511
Hoo!

17:12.732 --> 17:13.798
Yes, hello, police?

17:13.800 --> 17:19.069
Yes, it would seem like I
have a dead body in my office.

17:20.540 --> 17:22.073
Yeah, I would appreciate
it if you could

17:22.075 --> 17:23.674
send someone to take care of it.

17:25.678 --> 17:26.810
Thank you kindly.

18:17.430 --> 18:19.113
Hey!

18:19.114 --> 18:20.797
