- It's a free country, man.

18:20.800 --> 18:22.567
Yeah, so is jail, pal.

18:22.569 --> 18:23.569
Come on.

18:24.804 --> 18:27.538
Hey, what did I say?

18:27.540 --> 18:29.474
You don't me to
hurt you, do you?

18:31.344 --> 18:32.610
Poor Claire.

18:32.612 --> 18:36.747
You must remember,
technically Dominican Order,

18:37.750 --> 18:40.218
or if you're up for the
pun, Helms of the Lord.

18:42.856 --> 18:45.423
Either way, I'm the poor
poor cloistered nun.

18:46.593 --> 18:48.326
Quickly, come in.

18:57.753 --> 18:59.336
I have left the papal
enclosure of the monastery

18:59.339 --> 19:01.839
for my medical emergency.

19:03.443 --> 19:06.377
My appointment with
the big placebo.

19:08.181 --> 19:09.181
God.

19:11.918 --> 19:13.784
That is a big cross.

19:16.489 --> 19:19.457
Better to remind me of my
lord when my thoughts stray.

19:23.663 --> 19:25.263
Please, follow me.

19:32.906 --> 19:33.906
Have a seat.

19:42.282 --> 19:43.881
Ingenuity of the past.

19:45.218 --> 19:48.586
See, this is an ancient
Chinese candle clock.

19:55.428 --> 19:58.629
As it burns down in
10 minute intervals,

19:58.631 --> 20:01.632
the weights fall into
the sounding plate below

20:02.502 --> 20:05.770
notifying me of time left.

20:10.243 --> 20:12.510
The final weight
at the hour's end

20:12.512 --> 20:15.580
pings distinctly as
if a lovely lullaby.

20:31.731 --> 20:33.998
Um, I feel a
little uncomfortable.

20:35.868 --> 20:39.270
Would you mind if I
remove my wet wimple?

20:52.018 --> 20:53.584
Are you comfortable now?

20:56.489 --> 20:58.322
I'm dead to the world.

21:00.727 --> 21:02.844
My five years spent as a novice

21:02.845 --> 21:04.962
deemed me ready by the
abest to join the monastery.

21:07.467 --> 21:10.334
I've accepted, secretly
hiding a skeptical heart.

21:11.904 --> 21:14.572
My solemn vow is to
the spiritual life

21:14.574 --> 21:18.476
but it's left me with more
questions than answers.

21:19.746 --> 21:20.746
For instance?

21:21.981 --> 21:23.014
Why am I here?

21:24.384 --> 21:25.550
'Cause you wanna be here.

21:25.551 --> 21:26.717
I mean, why is anybody here?

21:26.719 --> 21:27.719
What's the point?

21:29.856 --> 21:32.657
So religion hasn't given
you the answers you need.

21:33.493 --> 21:35.393
I'm sorry to say, no.

21:35.395 --> 21:37.995
Loved ones die and then they
leave us behind to mourn.

21:37.997 --> 21:39.930
What great plan is that?

21:40.667 --> 21:42.233
I don't understand it.

21:42.234 --> 21:43.800
I mean, I'd rather
not exist than to have

21:43.803 --> 21:46.370
this understanding
of not understanding.

21:46.372 --> 21:48.472
It's just too painful.

21:50.476 --> 21:55.346
So you have any
enjoyment in life at all?

21:55.348 --> 21:59.350
Split seconds don't erase
history nor stop the future.

22:01.888 --> 22:05.656
I dare to venture
into the taboo land

22:05.658 --> 22:08.492
of blasphemy to
whisper my doubts.

22:11.764 --> 22:13.764
Maybe there is no God.

22:15.835 --> 22:17.568
Oh God, I said it.

22:18.971 --> 22:20.905
Maybe it's only imagination,

22:20.906 --> 22:22.840
that we urgently try to
fill the darkness with.

22:25.511 --> 22:26.711
I don't know.

22:29.782 --> 22:31.582
