who would argue

22:31.584 --> 22:33.584
that you are
clinically depressed

22:33.586 --> 22:36.520
and not open to any
divine surrounding you.

22:38.658 --> 22:40.391
And you say?

22:40.393 --> 22:43.527
Boltzmann brain paradox
leans on your shoulders

22:43.529 --> 22:45.696
as you face your abyss.

22:45.698 --> 22:46.997
Self-awareness, more likely,

22:46.999 --> 22:48.866
to have formed
out of chaos, huh?

22:50.103 --> 22:54.472
Facing my alter ego Atlas,
supporting the heavens.

22:54.474 --> 22:56.407
So you're the
doctor, which am I?

22:58.678 --> 23:02.947
Dogma only knows the lie,
philosophy goes both directions.

23:02.949 --> 23:04.448
No philosophy.

23:04.450 --> 23:09.086
When I die, I'm dead and I'm
not coming back to argue.

23:27.840 --> 23:32.843
I guess my imaginary god doesn't
like me talking that way.

23:36.048 --> 23:38.749
See, why must I wear this cross?

23:38.751 --> 23:40.918
What have I been
saying, what am I doing?

23:40.920 --> 23:43.621
I am tortured by his torture

23:43.623 --> 23:45.890
and my eternal pain
knows my own soul

23:45.892 --> 23:48.058
by I can not feel him back.

23:49.462 --> 23:51.595
I cannot touch the
warmth of his skin.

23:52.799 --> 23:54.799
To have him hold me.

23:54.801 --> 23:57.668
Only to feel the
cold prickly brass

23:57.670 --> 24:00.037
that this really
breeds not enough.

24:00.039 --> 24:02.907
It's not enough.

24:02.909 --> 24:04.809
I feel really hot.

24:04.811 --> 24:07.144
I feel like, I feel
like I'm suffocating.

24:32.805 --> 24:33.805
Please.

24:35.074 --> 24:36.074
Help me.

25:07.006 --> 25:08.572
Please help me.

25:13.880 --> 25:14.880
Hold me.

25:16.215 --> 25:17.215
Please.

25:18.951 --> 25:19.951
Hold me.

25:21.821 --> 25:25.089
I need to feel the
tangible love of man

25:25.091 --> 25:28.092
and not just a symbol of a man.

25:28.094 --> 25:29.094
Please.

25:30.830 --> 25:32.963
Please lay me down.

25:32.965 --> 25:34.698
Make me feel real.

25:43.042 --> 25:47.311
Make love to me.

25:47.313 --> 25:49.613
Hold me for the first time.

25:49.615 --> 25:51.148
I think that I am troubled.

25:51.150 --> 25:53.050
I don't wanna go
inside the booth.

26:38.030 --> 26:39.030
Thank you.

26:48.374 --> 26:50.174
Forgive me, Father.

26:51.711 --> 26:53.243
For I have sinned.

27:19.205 --> 27:21.005
You are forgiven.

29:15.821 --> 29:16.987
Ah, a magician.

29:18.057 --> 29:19.056
My hobby.

29:19.058 --> 29:22.092
My profession,
Detective Lighthaze.

29:23.529 --> 29:25.529
