36:27.051 --> 36:28.350
Cheers.

36:34.493 --> 36:35.892
Please, come in.

36:38.564 --> 36:40.497
How do you know
the good detective?

36:42.568 --> 36:46.436
One night stand
became a two night stand

36:46.438 --> 36:50.640
and three night
stand and I haven't

36:50.642 --> 36:53.510
