night for anybody.

37:04.656 --> 37:06.456
And what about you?

37:08.260 --> 37:09.726
Why does he come to see you?

37:10.829 --> 37:14.965
Sorry, that's
doctor-patient privilege.

37:16.468 --> 37:18.468
All I gotta do
is ask, ya know?

37:19.304 --> 37:21.571
Well, why haven't you?

37:22.941 --> 37:24.007
