38:03.048 --> 38:05.048
Unless you're a card geek,

38:07.452 --> 38:12.589
52 cards, 13 ranks
each of the four suits,

38:13.625 --> 38:17.727
diamonds, clubs,
spades, and hearts.

38:25.771 --> 38:27.387
Ace of spades.

38:27.388 --> 38:29.004
Unique with its
large ornate spade.

38:29.875 --> 38:31.675
Said to be the death card.

38:34.746 --> 38:36.012
The king of hearts.

38:36.014 --> 38:39.783
The only king
without a mustache.

38:40.786 --> 38:43.386
